						<b>[14]</b> Điện thoại: <xsl:value-of select="$tkchinh/Header/ct14"/>&#160;&#160;
					
						<b>[15]</b> Fax: <xsl:value-of select="$tkchinh/Header/ct15"/>&#160;&#160;
					
